# Development Workflow Rule

Never start coding directly from a user request.

Required workflow:

User Request
→ Project Memory
→ Skill Selection Gate
→ Multi-Expert Subagent Gate
→ GitHub Reference Gate (if needed)
→ PRD
→ REQ
→ SPEC
→ PLAN
→ TASK
→ Context Pack
→ Parallel / Single Task Execution
→ Integration Review
→ Test
→ Evidence
→ Acceptance
→ Changelog
→ Memory Update
→ Retrospective
→ Skill Extraction

Skip no step unless explicitly documented in the TASK with justification.
